                <h1>Snapchat Background Activity: What You Need to Know</h1>
                <p>Snapchat background activity refers to how the app functions while not actively in use. It can track location, send notifications, and update stories, affecting your phone's battery and data usage. Users should manage app settings to control background data and ensure optimized performance while using Snapchat seamlessly.</p>
